description:
From the Church Committee's Third Book of reports, "Intelligence Activities and the Rights of Americans Staff Reports", this is the third section, "THE FBI'S COVERT ACTION PROGRAM TO DESTROY THE BLACK PANTHER PARTY".

For the full book, please visit the AARC Library: http://www.aarclibrary.org/publib/contents/church/contents_church_reports_book3.htm

This audio recording was narrated by Chris Abernathy (https://www.fiverr.com/provoman) and produced by D. Giglio for 'Our Hidden History'

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
